title: Sample Book, Alfred Peats No. 4, 1908
description: Collection of patterns put together by Alfred Peats. Each of the patterns is part of a matched set consisting of a sidewall, frieze and ceiling paper. Each design is shown in mulitple colorways.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Alfred Peats No. 4, 1908; Manufactured by Alfred Peats Company ; USA; machine-printed paper, embossed; 47.5 x 39 cm (18 11/16 x 15 3/8 in.); 1979-46-1-1/139
